      "message": "lgtm but:\n\n1. Is it possible to teach bbagent not to do overlapping UpdateBuild calls? It\u0027s kind of useless.\n2. Maybe we need to add a sequence number or something to UpdateBuild and make the server reject out-of-order calls?",
